				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2020 04:04:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><strong>Spilled Milk</strong><br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600578969" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;">▷ <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5990" target="_blank">Entry for DAY ONE</a></strong> ◁</p> <p style="text-align: center;">▷ <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scattersomnia" target="_blank">Entry for DAY THREE</a></strong> ◁</p> <hr /> <p>This is a <strong>Tale</strong> entry for <strong>DAY TWO</strong> of the <strong>144-Hour Jam Contest Two</strong>! The theme was <strong>Delicious</strong>. As I mentioned in my entry for day one (follow the link above!), the GOI I am focusing on is Oneiroi. This time around, I had a lot of difficulty getting this thing sorted out until very near the deadline (this is a boldpost). It's sloppy, but I'm mostly happy with what I accomplished!</p> <p>I also got to write Moosphere, Inc.! You can see the article they were first mentioned in here: <strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3739">SCP-3739</a></strong></p> <p>This article is set in the <strong>Broken Masquerade</strong> and takes place shortly after SCP-3739. I intend on polishing this up after the contest!</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Critters &amp; Beta Readers</strong></span></p> <p>▷ <strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3656445&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600578969" alt="Ellie3" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3656445)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ellie3" >Ellie3</a></span></strong>, for reading over a brief, early version of this.</p> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Sources</strong></span></p> <ul> <li><strong>1: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/54272628@N00/2749397067" target="_blank">many-ꙮd-gf</a> – CC BY 2.0</strong></li> <li><strong>2: <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:%D0%A1%D0%B8%D1%8F%D1%8E%D1%89%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D1%80%D1%8B%D0%B1%D0%B0_(Cosmic_blue_tetra_fish).jpg" target="_blank">virtuallight</a> – CC BY-SA 4.0</strong></li> <li><strong>3: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/48600098077@N01/7471112808" target="_blank">CRAB LORD</a> – CC BY 2.0</strong></li> <li><strong>4: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/59973753@N03/6022754597" target="_blank">tinkleschubbyghost</a> – CC BY 2.0</strong></li> <li><strong>5: <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/141143347@N08/46917579105" target="_blank">TheodoreGL</a> – CC BY 2.0</strong></li> </ul> <ul> <li>&quot;<strong>Ighruithrh'dhren</strong>&quot; is from a Eldritch name generator.</li> <li>The &quot;<strong>AMBROSE MINDSCAPE</strong>&quot; menu teaser uses some code from <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ambrose-thorn-valley" target="_blank">Ambrose Thorn Valley</a></strong>, written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3489662&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600578969" alt="mayoculpa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3489662)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" >mayoculpa</a></span> with code repurposed from <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600578969" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span>.</li> <li>The character &quot;<strong>Chaz Ambrose</strong>&quot; was created by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1956625&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600578969" alt="DrChandra" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1956625)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drchandra" >DrChandra</a></span>. The GOI &quot;<strong>Ambrose Restaurants</strong>&quot; was created by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2048131&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600578969" alt="Proasek" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2048131)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" >Proasek</a></span>. This article is my take on them from an alternate angle.</li> </ul> </div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;Close</a></div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/floppyphoenix">If you liked this, check out my Author Page!</a></strong></span></p> 
				 	]]>
